{
  "stem": "322.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I, I sensed that this is not going to work either way, because every time you get out of the-- get out of your apartment, you know, you get picked up by a Russian patrol and taken to, to, to City Hall.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they work you all day and give you a bowl of soup maybe and then send you back again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the next day the same thing happens over again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I decided to leave and I went, went to Slovakia, from Slovakia to Prague, and then from there the Zionist organization [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] got us moved to Germany.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I ended up in a, in a displaced persons camp, Eschwege by castle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was in constant search.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never would give up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Somehow, I don't know, I thought I had someone to look for, so I could never sit still.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And even though I was settled in the displaced persons camp, most of the time I traveled.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went looking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went to another displaced persons camp, and I tried to find out at least from those who were with my father or were with my brother or knew what happened to my mother and my two sisters and so on.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, and I did get quite a bit of details.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that at least-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I would say that helped make a comeback, because I felt that I'm going to live here for one purpose, to know more and more and more and more, day by day, each day what did happen.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why did it happen?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why did it have to happen?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then perhaps how is it possible to prevent it from happening again?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this is what kept you going.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
